OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782749904
OL,3,CWhite working-class children 'not
OL,4,Cserved by education system', inquiry
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FOnce-in-a-generation reforms are
OL,8,Fneeded to fix an education system "not
OL,9,Fset up to serve white working-class
OL,10,Fchildren and families", an independent
OL,11,Finquiry concluded on Monday.
OL,13,FIt was commissioned last summer to
OL,14,Fdetermine why such pupils are the
OL,15,Flowest-performing large demographic in
OL,16,FEngland.
OL,26,@pD@cOUrD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
