OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782749904
OL,3,CWhite working-class children 'not
OL,4,Cserved by education system', inquiry
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FInquiry co-chairs Baroness Estelle
OL,8,FMorris and Sir Hamid Patel said the
OL,9,Fissues identified in the report
OL,10,F"cannot be explained away by low
OL,11,Faspiration or lack of effort", and
OL,12,Fcannot be "solved by schools alone".
OL,14,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,15,Fsaid generations had been "robbed" of
OL,16,Fopportunity, adding: "The communities
OL,17,Fin this report are my communities.
OL,19,F"I know what they've given this
OL,20,Fcountry and what this country has
OL,21,Ffailed to give back."
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@]O]tD@KOUtD@cO]wD@[OUwD@bO]xD@
