OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782749904
OL,3,CWhite working-class children 'not
OL,4,Cserved by education system', inquiry
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe Independent Inquiry into White
OL,8,FWorking-Class Educational Outcomes was
OL,9,Fcommissioned by the multi-academy
OL,10,Ftrust Star Academies, and is supported
OL,11,Fby the Department for Education.
OL,13,FThousands of young people and their
OL,14,Fparents as well as hundreds of
OL,15,Fteachers were interviewed for the
OL,16,Finquiry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
