OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782749905
OL,3,CWhite working-class children 'not
OL,4,Cserved by education system', inquiry
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FAmong its findings, the inquiry
OL,8,Fdetermined white working-class
OL,9,Fcommunities and the education system
OL,10,Fhad different viewpoints as to how
OL,11,Feach defines success and the purpose
OL,12,Fof education.
OL,14,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
