PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782749905
OL,3,CWhite working-class children 'not
OL,4,Cserved by education system', inquiry
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FIt said that while many families place
OL,8,Fgreater importance on the social
OL,9,Fexperience of school and call for more
OL,10,Fimportance to be placed on vocational
OL,11,Foptions for students, such as
OL,12,Fapprenticeships, the education system
OL,13,Foften emphasised academic progression
OL,14,Fto higher education.
OL,16,FIn its 24 recommendations, the inquiry
OL,17,Fcalls for more early-years support,
OL,18,Fimproved mental health support and
OL,19,Frestrictions on smartphone use in
OL,20,Fschools.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782749905
OL,3,CWhite working-class children 'not
OL,4,Cserved by education system', inquiry
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FIt also says improvements are needed
OL,8,Fin how the system defines and
OL,9,Fprioritises white working-class
OL,10,Feducational outcomes, urges an
OL,11,Fextension of 30 hours' free childcare
OL,12,Fto all disadvantaged families not
OL,13,Fcurrently eligible, and also calls for
OL,14,Fa massive expansion in apprenticeship
OL,15,Fopportunities in white working-class
OL,16,Fcommunities.
OL,18,FBaroness Morris and Sir Hamid said
OL,19,Faddressing these issues "will require
OL,20,Fsustained national effort over many
OL,21,Fyears".
OL,26,@{D@YOU}D@FO]
