FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782749905
OL,3,CWhite working-class children 'not
OL,4,Cserved by education system', inquiry
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThey said: "The challenge set out in
OL,8,Fthis report is significant. But so too
OL,9,Fis the opportunity.
OL,11,F"Every child in this country deserves
OL,12,Fto feel that education is for them,
OL,13,Fthat their future matters, and that
OL,14,Fsuccess is achievable regardless of
OL,15,Fwhere they come from."
